This is for producing templates {{tl|bra}}, {{tl|ket}}, and {{tl|bra-ket}}. It can also produce [[quantum state]] vectors in [[bra–ket notation]], using wikicode, ideally with {{tl|math}}, as an alternative to [[LaTeX]] in <nowiki><math></nowiki> mode, but using this template ( <nowiki>{{braket}}</nowiki> ) is more clumsy than the simpler and more directly applicable <nowiki>{{bra}}, {{ket}}, and {{bra-ket}}</nowiki>.

==Application==

There are three parameters, use as many as needed in this order:
